  "desc": "<p>如今几乎绝迹的长柄钻机，常用于勘探与石料切割雕刻作业。</p>",
  "iconUrl": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/10/12/82021897/4bfc21303d8ff98cd546aae980b55090_3304700411281800543.png",
